videos.description: Virginia Tech's Josh Jackson fakes a hand off and sees a gap and runs in for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Hokies QB fakes a hand off for TD

videos.description:
Rafael Araujo-Lopes avoids defenders with 
a nice spinning move and runs the ball in for a Panthers' touchdown.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh's Araujo-Lopes ties up game with TD

videos.description: Panthers' Ben Dinucci scampers under pressure and throws an interception to Virginia Tech's Reggie Floyd.
videos.headline: Hokies' Floyd picks off third pass of season

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Josh Jackson pass is intercepted by Pittsburgh's Avonte Maddox.
videos.headline: Panthers' Maddox picks off Hokies

videos.description: Young Hokies fans dabbing to celebrate the missed 33-yard field goal attempt by Panthers kicker Alex Kessman.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech fans celebrating missed Pittsburgh FG

videos.description: Punter Ryan Winslow finds 4th string tight end Nathan Bossory for a Panthers' touchdown.
videos.headline: Trick play leads to Panthers TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Greg Stroman picks off Pittsburgh's Kenny Pickett's pass, and dodges multiple tackles for a 12-yard return.
videos.headline: Hokies' Stroman with impressive interception return

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Greg Stroman makes a great last second read, and breaks up the pass intended for Pittsburgh's Jester Weah in the end zone.
videos.headline: Hokies' Stroman with the play of the game

videos.description: Hokies' Reggie Floyd makes the huge tackle on 4th down preventing the Panthers from scoring as time expires.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's defense stops Pittsburgh at goal line for win
